程序包 org.springframework.web.client.reactive

Provides a reactive WebClient that builds on top of the org.springframework.http.client.reactive reactive HTTP adapter layer.

请参阅: 说明

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    ClientRequest<T>
    Represents a typed, immutable, client-side HTTP request, as executed by the WebClient.
    ClientRequest.BodyBuilder
    Defines a builder that adds a body to the request entity.
    ClientRequest.HeadersBuilder<B extends ClientRequest.HeadersBuilder<B>>
    Defines a builder that adds headers to the request.
    ClientResponse
    Represents an HTTP response, as returned by the WebClient.
    ClientResponse.Headers
    Represents the headers of the HTTP response.
    ExchangeFilterFunction
    Represents a function that filters an exchange function.
    ExchangeFunction
    Represents a function that exchanges a request for a (delayed) ClientResponse.
    WebClient
    Reactive Web client supporting the HTTP/1.1 protocol.
    WebClient.Builder
    A mutable builder for a WebClient.
    WebClientStrategies
    Defines the strategies to be used by the WebClient.
    WebClientStrategies.Builder
    A mutable builder for a WebClientStrategies.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ExchangeFilterFunctions
    Implementations of ExchangeFilterFunction that provide various useful request filter operations, such as basic authentication, error handling, etc.
  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    WebClientException
    Exception published by WebClient in case of errors.
